commits.author: Dawid Weiss
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Called once for every document matching a query, with the unbased document * number. * *

* Note: This is called in an inner search loop. For good search performance, * implementations of this method should not call {@link Searcher#doc(int)} or * {@link org.apache.lucene.index.IndexReader#document(int)} on every hit. * Doing so can slow searches by an order of magnitude or more. */ public abstract void collect(int doc) throws IOException;
